    <item>
      <title>华尔街对美国股票的冰冷变成了冰冷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/yardeni-says-us-stock-swoon-offers-great-buying-opportunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街的预报员正在对美国股票进行冰冷，并告诉投资者避免购买抛售，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统的历史性贸易战使经济衰退的幽灵造成了抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/yardeni-says-us-stock-swoon-offers-great-buying-opportunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 06:13:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关税锤金属和矿工的关税，铜暴跌超过5％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/copper-set-for-weekly-slide-as-tariffs-tarnish-metals-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜跌至每吨9,000美元以下的交易量超过5％，这是2022年7月以来最大的下降，因为担心贸易战争恶化的影响引起了工业金属和采矿股票的巨大抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/copper-set-for-weekly-slide-as-tariffs-tarnish-metals-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 03:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油滑坡至四年低点的关税和欧佩克供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克+出现惊喜产量增加以及全球贸易战的惊人产量增加之后，石油在四年内跌至最低，这也使商品市场从金属到天然气都震撼了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500期货潜水3％作为抛售增长势头：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票期货跌倒了，表明华尔街又遭受了巨大的损失，随着中国开始在全球贸易战争的下一个阶段，债券与美国产品的新关税开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
